detailedDescription.articleBody:
Letitia Jane Dean is an English actress and singer. She is best known for her portrayal of Sharon Watts in the BBC soap opera, EastEnders. An original cast member from 1985 to 1995, she reprised the role from 2001 to 2006, and again from 2012 onwards.
Her other television roles include Grange Hill, Brookside, The Hello Girls, and Lucy Sullivan is Getting Married. In 2007, she participated in the fifth series of the BBC dance competition Strictly Come Dancing, finishing fourth.
